{"tid":1216583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實造成今日呢個局面嘅唔（只）係政府.......","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:55:10.000Z","uid":172797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2fea849f0f93b2d60881daf2d9564189f80c9a","tid":1216583,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"點解我地係阻止開立法會，而唔係相信代議士？<br />\n<br />\n點解立法會由制衡政府嘅工具變左政府嘅工具？<br />\n<br />\n點解立法會議員唔係反映主流民意？<br />\n<br />\n點解撐買票種票禮義廉嘅廢老仲大行其道？<br />\n<br />\n其實造成今日呢個局面嘅唔（只）係政府....... <br />\n<br />\n因為我地（部分人）唔積極投票啊，2016年投票率創新高，但都得58％，姐係一百萬人上街，可能得60萬人有投票。如果多40萬非建制票，立法會一早係公民社會據點啦屌！！<br />\n<br />\n咩叫廢青? 唔投票就叫廢青！<br />\n<br />\n7月2日deadline 登記做選民<br />\n<br />\n和理非又好 不合作又好 勇武都好<br />\n<br />\n快d呼籲身邊政治冷感嘅朋友投票啦！！"},{"pid":"14c8ffb05831e1b16f81fef7caf096a9f22bf8df","tid":1216583,"uid":249049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"其實講真淨係功能組別都收哂你哋皮 點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a03429fc6e07bbe2d153f6cd9dbed44ceffe4a","tid":1216583,"uid":172797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14c8ffb05831e1b16f81fef7caf096a9f22bf8df","tid":1216583,"uid":249049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"其實講真淨係功能組別都收哂你哋皮 點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"兄弟此言差矣，分組點票架麻，我地要力保地區直選否決權！"},{"pid":"42b7feb0459900e4526e99c0ce2e6768a879379b","tid":1216583,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9004ac9de8b62ab08dc80e51106a2768d7a6549f","tid":1216583,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c312008166270629ebe05f6aa328e129356f2e6","tid":1216583,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"